  "prompt": "Is it just me, or is Two and a Half Men really the best comedy series?",
  "response": "It's not just you! *Two and a Half Men* has a dedicated fan base and is often praised for its humor, particularly during the Charlie Sheen years. Its sitcom-style comedy, sharp one-liners, and quirky characters (like Alan, Charlie, and later Walden) made it a hit for many viewers. That said, comedy is subjective, and what one person finds hilarious, another might not. There are plenty of other comedy series\u2014like *Friends*, *The Office*, *Parks and Recreation*, or *Brooklyn Nine-Nine*\u2014that people might argue are the \"best.\" It all depends on your taste! What do you love most about *Two and a Half Men*?",
